title: Arnette Introduces The Change Up -- Two Sunglasses In One
description:
The Change Up is one of the most diverse and stylish frames in the A.C.E.S. (Arnette Creative Exchange System) line, so it's only natural we had Todd Richards and a special guest explain what they're all about.

The Change Up is the first 8-base wrap A.C.E.S. frame. Like all A.C.E.S. models, it comes with an extra set of interchangeable arms.

What's unique to the Change Up is that one set of arms is thick and one set is thinner, allowing for the ultimate in custom style-enhancing radness. With interchangeable arms that allow for two completely different profiles, The Change Up is truly two shades in one.

The Change Up features an incredibly durable Grilamid frame, lightweight polycarbonate lenses and a unique style no one can touch.

Check out the full range of color options here http://www.arnette.com/products/chang....
